summary: Transforms General Tullius... into a WOMAN!
descriptionHtml:
The only thing General Tullius ever wanted was to destroy those lawless Nordic Stormcloaks and their leader, Jarl Ulfress Stormcloak. 

But secretly, he always had another wish... 

TO BECOME A WOMAN! And a... not so sexy one at that! Now, his dream came true with the help of a mysterious persona\'s magical potion. 

The only drawback of such, is that he still has his sexy man-growl, but he loves his voice too much to change it. 

This one didn\'t come out nearly as well as the Ulfric one, but I guess its an Imperial thing...

*This is purely a joke! I made this because it was the easiest mod to make, ever*
author: Kasaru
